description: Variation to drawing nos. to approved application 14/0914/FUL to allow for changes to layout and number of proposed residential buildings and an increase in the amount of landscaped area. (The amendments relate to primarily to some minor adjustment in the height of some of the buildings, the orientation of the outer buildings, amalgamation of the two previous central buildings into a single building, provision of a single point of access from Broom Road, provision of all parking in the basement and an enhanced area of landscaping.
